{"tid":2238343,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國國內外知名的作曲家們參與TWICE新專輯","createTime":"2020-10-11T05:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T13:08:02.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef51c9388e3ea6149880cb358f3f1f17467dbd8","tid":2238343,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ej9ZLecU4AEhsjO?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEj9ZLecU4AEhsjO%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dorig&h=9ffc253f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n志效-娜璉-Sana-多賢-彩瑛參與作詞<br />\n11日，JYP方面通過官方SNS公開了TWICE超話正規二輯《Eyes wide open》的Tracklist，包括朴軫永在內，Dua Lipa、沈恩地、Kenzie、Heize等韓國國內外知名的作曲家們參與了專輯的製作。在新專輯中，包括主打曲《I CAN&rsquo;T STOP ME》在內共收錄了13首歌曲。另外，成員志效、娜璉、Sana、多賢、彩瑛單獨參與了收錄曲的作詞，將TWICE獨有的感覺融入到音樂中<br />\n<br />\n主打歌當然唔少得我地DADDY填詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8259bd8ac7c696655aa10e902516f25764a2032","tid":2238343,"uid":177639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"GG"},{"pid":"fec0471dacae158fb054459548722ba16206cee8","tid":2238343,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"腎b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8a8391bfb55771a2b0313e937d0c5beb40f364","tid":2238343,"uid":255310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fec0471dacae158fb054459548722ba16206cee8","tid":2238343,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"腎b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"清識啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=